  "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p> \n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 24.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; text-indent: -24.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\">\n <!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">一、</span>\n  <!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">台灣同志諮詢熱線網站連結應從教材中刪除。</span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 24.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; text-indent: -24.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">\n  <!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">二、</span>\n  <!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">幼獅出版社之教材已違反兒少福利法第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">43</span><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">條。</span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 24.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; text-indent: -24.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">\n  <!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">三、</span>\n  <!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: '新細明體',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 新細明體; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">教育部失職容許該網站入教材。</span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>",
